Changelog
-----------
v1.2.1 May 10th 2023
Hotfix for missing resource file

v1.2 April 23rd 2023
Flatpak support added
Fixed failure condition if linbox folder exists but contains no ini file

v1.15 April 21st 2023
Changed to Qt Resource file instead of hardcoded relative path
Added menu bar
Added about page
Added version number to main window title
Cleaned up messy folder structure

v1.14 April 21st 2023
Fixed keyboard input handler, ditched regex, use python translate. Now ' ', '/' & '\' are replaced with '-'

v1.13 April 21st 2023
Fixed issue with config handler logic, it no longer nukes the entire file when deleting a VM

V1.12 April 21st 2023
Final (hopefully) pass at UI overhaul
Changed listWidget selection colour to something less bright

V1.11 April 20th 2023
Minor tweaks to UI and added QOL stuff like tooltips and tab ordering
Changed xdg implementation to xdgenvpy, xdg-base-dirs would randomly stop working
Started creating packing/build files

V1.1 April 20th 2023
Total UI overhaul, remade the entire UI from scratch

V1.01 April 19th 2023
Fixed entering special characters in name entry box crash

V1.0 - April 19th 2023
Initial release
